  "pokedexDescription": "Ludikappa are solitary predators that lure travellers deep into bogs with the sweet scent of the flower on its head. When its prey gets too close to the water it drags them down into the deep, never to be seen again. The flower on its head makes a smell so pleasent it is said no one can resist its aroma. For this reason many perfumes use this flower as a part of their recipes.",
